<node id="Program Translation And Human Language Translation Comparison">
  <data key="d0">Program Translation And Human Language Translation Comparison</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">An explanatory analogy that maps the technical processes of program compilation and interpretation to real-world human cross-language translation scenarios to simplify understanding of the two program translation modes.</data>
