<node id="13s frame of Compilation Principles course introductory agenda slide (China University MOOC) (image)">
  <data key="d0">13s frame of Compilation Principles course introductory agenda slide (China University MOOC) (image)</data>
  <data key="d1">image</data>
  <data key="d2">This NUDT China University MOOC lecture frame displays the lesson's introduction agenda alongside the speaking instructor, matching the audio that announces the lesson will cover compiler definitions and learning rationale first.</data>
