<edge source="Interpreter Program" target="Interpretation">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The interpreter program follows and implements the interpretation translation method to process the original program statements.</data>
  <data key="d9">Follows,implements</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Interpreter Program" target="Original Computer Program">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The interpreter program sequentially extracts each individual statement from the original computer program, translates it, runs it, and proceeds until all program statements are fully processed.</data>
  <data key="d9">Processes,executes,translates</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Interpreter Program" target="Machine Instructions">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The interpreter program converts each statement extracted from the original computer program into corresponding machine instructions, then executes those low-level instructions directly to get the program running result.</data>
  <data key="d9">Translates,executes</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compilation" target="Full Chinese Equivalent Operation Manual">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The compilation translation mode generates and outputs a full Chinese operation manual that is fully equivalent to the original English version.</data>
  <data key="d9">Generates,produces</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compilation" target="Professional Translator">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The compilation translation mode is demonstrated via the scenario where the translator generates the complete full Chinese operation manual from the original English version.</data>
  <data key="d9">Is demonstrated via scenario of</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compilation" target="Program Translation And Human Language Translation Comparison">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The analogy maps the compilation program translation method to the human translation scenario where a full complete translated manual is generated for later independent use.</data>
  <data key="d9">Maps,illustrates</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compilation" target="Quiz: Compilation Vs. Interpretation">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The concept of Compilation is marked with a prominent red checkmark as the correct answer (option A) of the Quiz: Compilation Vs. Interpretation.</data>
  <data key="d9">Mark as correct answer</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ff0eb7c8503f6f576c5dbe6ae9289e07</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935568</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compilation" target="Cartoon Analogy Demonstration Diagram">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Cartoon Analogy Demonstration Diagram uses the scenario of a translator producing a completely equivalent Chinese manual from an original English manual to intuitively illustrate the core working logic of the compilation concept.</data>
  <data key="d9">Demonstrate,Illustrate</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-ff0eb7c8503f6f576c5dbe6ae9289e07</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
