<edge source="Interpretation" target="Full Chinese Equivalent Operation Manual">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The interpretation translation mode does not produce any standalone full Chinese operation manual equivalent to the entire original English equipment operation manual.</data>
  <data key="d9">Does not generate</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
