  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Interpretation" target="Professional Translator">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The interpretation translation mode is demonstrated via the scenario where the translator translates each single sentence of the English manual one by one, with the operator acting immediately after each translation.</data>
  <data key="d9">Is demonstrated via scenario of</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Interpretation" target="Program Translation And Human Language Translation Comparison">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The analogy maps the interpretation program translation method to the human translation scenario where each source sentence is translated on demand for immediate execution, without producing a full standalone translated manual.</data>
  <data key="d9">Maps,illustrates</data>
  <data key="d10">doc-0964c36c2f3a13d4fcb742a671a493fd-chunk-001</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935038</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Interpretation" target="Quiz: Compilation Vs. Interpretation">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The concept of Interpretation is set as the unselected alternative option B of the Quiz: Compilation Vs. Interpretation.</data>
