<edge source="Compiler" target="High-Level Language Program">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A compiler accepts a high-level language program as its source input for processing.&lt;SEP&gt;A compiler processes a high-level language program and transforms it into an equivalent low-level language program&lt;SEP&gt;The compiler takes a complete high-level language program as its primary input at the start of the compilation process.&lt;SEP&gt;The compiler takes high-level language program as the input for its translation operation.</data>
  <data key="d9">Converts,Take as input,accepts as input,processes,takes as input,translate</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-5f5328057af8271fffc25a5e04150084&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c5ed2b863510eafd5fecdb97b44f6dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e10eb17b787da3ec7998622b93eaf3cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d85f67b63626aec731c1a8a42c23b26</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935568</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compiler" target="Low-Level Language Program">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A compiler converts the input high-level language program to generate an equivalent low-level language program as its output.&lt;SEP&gt;A compiler outputs an equivalent low-level language program after completing the translation operation&lt;SEP&gt;The compiler equivalently converts an input high-level language program to a functionally identical low-level language program as its primary output.&lt;SEP&gt;The compiler converts input high-level language program equivalently to low-level language program as its translation output.</data>
  <data key="d9">Equivalently convert to,Generates,converts to,generate output,generates,generates as output,outputs</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-5f5328057af8271fffc25a5e04150084&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5c5ed2b863510eafd5fecdb97b44f6dd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e10eb17b787da3ec7998622b93eaf3cf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8d85f67b63626aec731c1a8a42c23b26</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781935568</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
