<edge source="Machine Language Program" target="Program Execution Result">
  <data key="d7">2.0</data>
  <data key="d8">After a compiler generates a machine language program, executing that program produces the final Program Execution Result.&lt;SEP&gt;The machine language program is executed according to the workflow diagram to produce the final program execution result.</data>
